{"tid":499324,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣先可以個人開心啲？","createTime":"2017-12-14T16:17:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-14T19:12:52.000Z","uid":26279,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"4ae0184681c6b9772590dfcd8182b54d77c2439b","tid":499324,"uid":26279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T16:17:04.000Z","msg":"日日都勁灰 咩都提唔起勁<br />\n一到一個人個陣就勁唔開心<br />\n但對住人又冇乜野 <br />\n皮膚又好差生哂粒粒<br />\n更加唔鍾意自己<br />\n個人好無自信<br />\n有冇人可以教下我一個人點先會開心啲？<br />\n影相個陣永遠比人問做咩唔笑<br />\n生活圈子又越黎越細<br />\n唔想再係咁 生存得好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdcdecd2f51f77981f3164d512aa84c439fcffc5","tid":499324,"uid":26279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T16:19:26.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以理下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14b82f27a8b3cc4e1427303f56ef0024aa0f7653","tid":499324,"uid":25560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T16:20:10.000Z","msg":"去落後國家做義工"},{"pid":"6bca541422cfee45dca22dff25a8be3a9da3b739","tid":499324,"uid":19005,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T16:20:18.000Z","msg":"做多d幫助別人"},{"pid":"4e0d52fbefcbfcda2412d3841a7c1f7131ff9deb","tid":499324,"uid":25560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T16:20:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇人可以理下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n路過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/12.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aa211a3138fcc2ad8b3361af524382c90c275ba","tid":499324,"uid":2671,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T16:21:17.000Z","msg":"離開香港最直接"},{"pid":"3c620397b8642536caaf82ed7dccd34920fca5ad","tid":499324,"uid":160029,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T16:21:46.000Z","msg":"食多d開心果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf639936c9205f15271f7491a03a49a7549e52db","tid":